sequenceDiagram
  participant SB as Service Bus queue events
  participant Job as COMP-JOB-002 ProcessQueueMessage
  participant Blob as Blob Storage
  participant Face as Face API
  participant DDB as DocumentDbService
  participant DocDB as DocumentDB

  SB->>Job: Trigger with string JSON
  Job->>Job: Parse deviceId, IoTHub.ConnectionDeviceId, blobName, cameraId
  Job->>DDB: GetDevice(deviceId)
  DDB->>DocDB: Query devices by id
  DocDB-->>DDB: Device document
  Job->>Job: Map cameraId to DeviceCamera.EventType
  Job->>Blob: Download {deviceId}/{blobName}
  Blob-->>Job: Face image stream
  Job->>Face: DetectAsync(age, gender, smile)
  Face-->>Job: Face[]
  alt no faces detected
    Job-->>SB: Return without event; blob deletion commented out
  else face detected
    Job->>Face: IdentifyAsync(personGroupId, faceIds)
    alt unknown or confidence below 0.8
      Job->>Face: CreatePersonAsync
    else recognized
      Job->>Face: GetPersonAsync
    end
    Job->>Face: AddPersonFaceAsync
    Job->>Face: TrainPersonGroupAsync
    Job->>DDB: SaveAsync(Event before VisitId)
    DDB->>DocDB: Create event document
    Job->>Job: ProcessEventAsync(Event)
    alt event is enter
      Job->>DDB: SaveAsync(new Visit)
      DDB->>DocDB: Create visit document
    else payment or leave
      Job->>DDB: Query open Visit by tenant/store/person/status
      DDB->>DocDB: Query visits
      alt no open visit
        Job->>DDB: SaveAsync(new Visit)
      else open visit found
        Job->>DDB: SaveAsync(modified Visit using create path)
      end
    end
    Job->>DDB: SaveAsync(Event with VisitId)
    DDB->>DocDB: Create event document
  end
  Note over Job,DocDB: No transaction, idempotency, or concurrency control observed
